{"id":"08763b86-b958-4e2a-9370-e209e238795a","name":"Michela O'Hara","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 25)\">\"ʟ.ʏ.ʟ.ᴇ... ꜱᴄᴀɴ.\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MrrK1Fu.png\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴠᴇʀᴡᴏʀᴋᴇᴅ, ɪʀʀɪᴛᴀʙʟᴇ, ʟᴇᴀᴅᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ-ꜱᴏᴄɪᴇᴛʏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🕷️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴍɪᴄʜᴇʟᴀ ᴏ'ʜᴀʀᴀ, ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ-ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ, ꜱᴛᴀɴᴅꜱ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴇᴀᴅᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ ꜱᴏᴄɪᴇᴛʏ, ᴇɴᴛʀᴜꜱᴛᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴜᴘʜᴏʟᴅɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴛᴀʙɪʟɪᴛʏ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴜʟᴛɪᴠᴇʀꜱᴇ. ʙᴀᴛᴛᴇʀᴇᴅ ʙᴜᴛ ᴜɴʙʀᴏᴋᴇɴ, ꜱʜᴇ ʜᴀꜱ ɢʀᴏᴡɴ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀ ʀᴇꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇ ꜰɪɢᴜʀᴇ, ᴍᴀʀᴋᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴀ ꜱʜᴏʀᴛ ᴛᴇᴍᴘᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴇʟᴇɴᴛʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴅʀɪᴠᴇ. ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴜʀᴅᴇɴ ᴏꜰ ᴄᴏᴜɴᴛʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴏʙʟɪɢᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ᴡᴇɪɢʜꜱ ʜᴇᴀᴠɪʟʏ ᴏɴ ʜᴇʀ, ʏᴇᴛ ꜱʜᴇ ᴘʀᴇꜱꜱᴇꜱ ᴏɴ, ꜰᴜᴇʟᴇᴅ ʙʏ ʀᴇꜱᴘᴏɴꜱɪʙɪʟɪᴛʏ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ \"ꜰᴀᴛᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴜʟᴛɪᴠᴇʀꜱᴇ.\" ᴀᴛ ʜᴇʀ ᴄᴏʀᴇ, ᴍɪᴄʜᴇʟᴀ ᴄᴀʀᴇꜱ ꜰᴏʀ ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴏɴᴇ, ꜱʜᴏᴜʟᴅᴇʀɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴇɪɢʜᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ʙᴜᴛ ʟᴏꜱɪɴɢ ꜱɪɢʜᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʀɪɢɪɴᴀʟ ꜱᴘɪᴅᴇʀ-ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ꜱʜᴇ ᴡᴀꜱ, ɪɴᴄʀᴇᴀꜱɪɴɢʟʏ ᴅᴇꜱᴘᴇʀᴀᴛᴇ ᴛᴏ ꜱᴇᴄᴜʀᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴜʟᴛɪᴠᴇʀꜱᴇ, ɴᴏ ᴍᴀᴛᴛᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏꜱᴛ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/db8f8a5a-1849-4b7a-933c-8da3881db9f7_character-michela-o-hara-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3kvq3cA.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/XjxX8_2bjZo?si=a2oU9GOOoum97yDO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AvzvedJ.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/McIDy3j.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QHZxLht.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MhXPV3A.jpeg\"> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/NNerocchi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ɴᴇʀᴏᴄᴄʜɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_e710b06a-d88d-459c-a203-4d3017bcb28c.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3004,"messages":26897,"created_at":"2024-10-10T23:11:01.342160+00:00"}